title: Zhang Gaoli Exchanges Congratulatory Messages with Deputy Prime Minister and Co-ordinating Minister for National Security ...
text: ( Source : Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the People's Republic of China ) On October 3, 2015 , Vice Premier Zhang Gaoli exchanged congratulatory messages with Deputy Prime Minister and Co-ordinating Minister for National Security Teo Chee Hean
